  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd 22 \u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b87\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb2 \u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "It is not possible to call the petrol tanker till July 22 - Chakala Ratnayake",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chakala Ratnayake said that the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation did not have the capacity to bring in a petrol tanker until July 22.",
        "Meanwhile, he said an agreement with the World Bank to purchase 100,000 metric tons of gas needed for four months would be signed today or tomorrow.",
        "Chakala Ratnayake also said that between July 11 and July 15, only diesel for essential services would be available until a ship arrives."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "July 22",
          "label": "DATE"
        }
      ],
